      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">RMA: Mass Units for MT3DMS</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The mass units used in MT3DMS and MT3D-USGS are specified in the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">MODFLOW Options</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box. Select </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Model|MODFLOW Options</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and go to the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Options</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab. You can leave the units set to grams.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Mt3dmsRma10MassUnits.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title translate="true">MODFLOW Options dialog box showing mass units for MT3DMS.</title></image></para>
  </body>
